Tehreer-Android 1.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
com.mta.tehreer.bidi
Provides the classes necessary to apply Unicode Bidirectional Algorithm on text.
com.mta.tehreer.graphics
Provides the classes necessary for rendering typefaces.
com.mta.tehreer.opentype
Provides the classes necessary to shape the text into glyphs.
com.mta.tehreer.text
Provides the classes necessary to typeset simple or spanned text.
com.mta.tehreer.text.style
Provides classes for spans supported by Tehreer library.
com.mta.tehreer.util
Provides utility classes.
com.mta.tehreer.widget
Provides custom UI elements.
